title: Chasing the paperless office: how the engineering workplace is changing (London South Bank University)
text: ( Source: London South Bank University ) 05 October 2015 An event for students and young engineers will explore whether the engineering sector could adapt to working in an environment that is entirely paper-free A London South Bank University
